### Login administrador
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Perfil del usuario autenticado
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer PEGAR_TOKEN_AQUI

